title: Where Does Kyrie Go From Here?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and Israel Gutierrez debate what they are expecting with how Kyrie Irving and the Nets’ relationship will play out from here and what the Suns should do with Deandre Ayton.
